{"data":[{"date":"21:18 17/08","title":"Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U23 Malaysia 2-1 U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u Asiad 2018 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd khi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao Premier League, Son Heung Min \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. \"Ronaldo H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2 nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.</h2>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u Asiad 2018 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd khi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i sao Premier League, Son Heung Min \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8. \"Ronaldo H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 2 nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-the-hien-su-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-thang-nepal-168-194686.html\">Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nepal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/quang-hai-duoc-menh-danh-la-messi-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194685.html\">Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 'Messi Vi\u1ec7t Nam' \u1edf ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194684.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-malaysia-vs-u23-han-quoc-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194678.html\">U23 Malaysia 2-1 U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (KT): C\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n rung chuy\u1ec3n ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-indonesia-vs-u23-lao-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194676.html\">U23 Indonesia 3-0 U23 L\u00e0o (KT): Th\u1eafng d\u1ec5, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u1ea1i s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf ASIAD</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2482","checkdouble":"194701"},{"date":"22:12 17/08","title":"HLV Sarri l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/hlv-sarri-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Hazard s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea d\u00f9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hazard \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Chelsea sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9. Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y Hazard theo ch\u00e2n anh t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Goal cho bi\u1ebft Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn Hazard th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed CLB. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng v\u1ed9i v\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/HLV-Sarri-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Hazard s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Hazard v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng t\u1ef1 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Hazard r\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong 10 ng\u00e0y qua. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Real. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Hazard s\u1ebd \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ra s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield 3-0 cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Hazard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, Cesc Fabregas s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cFabregas \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea3\u201d, HLV Sarri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Fabregas. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u0111au g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nh\u01b0ng \u1edf g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3. Fabregas kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-doi-hinh-toi-uu-cua-chelsea-o-tran-gap-arsenal-172-194687.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1i \u01b0u c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-bom-tan-cua-chelsea-het-loi-172-194639.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e2n binh bom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u1ebft l\u1eddi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2481","checkdouble":"194702"},{"date":"23:24 17/08","title":"Milner: \"Liverpool c\u1ea7n tr\u1ecb ngay c\u0103n b\u1ec7nh th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/milner-liverpool-can-tri-ngay-can-benh-that-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Malcom kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa khi s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh si\u00eau sao Leo Messi v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ghi b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Boca Juniors.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean tranh c\u00fap Joan Gamper</span> (<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1edb s\u00e1ng l\u1eadp vi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Barcelona) n\u0103m nay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t b\u1edfi m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Malcom, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Bordeaux v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 41 tri\u1ec7u Euro, g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i b\u1edfi m\u00e0n l\u1eadt k\u00e8o Roma.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Malcom c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Malcom c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/malcom-toi-luon-muon-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n binh Malcom c\u1ee7a Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c Cules ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Malcom ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Boca Juniors, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea5y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o nh\u1ea5t. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u1ea1nh b\u00ean si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Leo Messi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00e2n th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Barca sau khi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i 21: \u201cT\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Messi, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. C\u00f2n g\u00ec tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi t\u00f4i ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft s\u00e2n Camp Nou, v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh anh \u1ea5y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">\u201cGi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c th\u1eadt r\u1ed3i, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu hay kh\u00f4ng \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa. N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u00e0ng h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf La Liga v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Barcelona s\u1ebd m\u1edf m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Deportivo Alaves.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\">Malcom \u2013 Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Barcelona</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft AS Roma. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh?</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2480","checkdouble":"194703"},{"date":"22:59 17/08","title":"R\u1ed9 tin Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd r\u1eddi SLNA \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t tay c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/7/ro-tin-que-ngoc-hai-se-roi-slna-de-vao-nam-thi-dau-voi-muc-lot-tay-cuc-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Khi m\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i V-League 2018 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac, \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd chia tay SLNA \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o Nam ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. </h2><h2>Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i r\u1eddi SLNA \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp CLB TP.HCM?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"R\u1ed9 tin Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i r\u1eddi SLNA \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t ta h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"R\u1ed9 tin Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i r\u1eddi SLNA \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t ta h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/que-ngoc-hai-noi-ve-ban-quyen-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd chia tay SLNA sau khi V-League 2018 k\u1ebft th\u00fac</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB SLNA m\u00e0 anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho CLB TP.HCM v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u00f3t tay c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi SLNA v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, hai b\u00ean v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i chung \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gia h\u1ea1n m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc \u1edf l\u1ea1i SLNA v\u00ec anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y CLB TP.HCM \u0111ang n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, n\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp CLB TP.HCM v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 l\u00f3t tay 8 t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng/n\u0103m. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB TP.HCM kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, song n\u00f3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n l\u00e0 \u201cchuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 th\u1eadt\u201d khi \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn s\u01a1 b\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y TP.HCM \u0111ang \u1edf nh\u00f3m x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i BXH v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd \u0111ang g\u1ea5p r\u00fat n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Miura gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2479","checkdouble":"194705"},{"date":"00:32 18/08","title":"Pochettino ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o nh\u1eefng coi th\u01b0\u1eddng Tottenham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/pochettino-phan-phao-nhung-coi-thuong-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Mauricio Pochettino \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean Spurs ra kh\u1ecfi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League n\u0103m nay ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Kh\u00f4ng mua v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u00e8m b\u00e1n, Tottenham m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed9c nh\u1ea5t v\u00f4 nh\u1ecb trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Premier League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u hay ho g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t CLB tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Champions League.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/pochettino-phan-phao-nhung-coi-thuong-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Pochettino n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Mauricio Pochettino v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Spurs, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1eb5n c\u00f3 trong tay. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh coi th\u01b0\u1eddng, g\u1ea1ch t\u00ean Spurs ra kh\u1ecfi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina sau k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cC\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh n\u00f3i t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea1m sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai, tuy nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i sau nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Newcastle v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Fulham s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, anh l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng h\u00f3a ra gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edbi c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n, l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng minh h\u01a1n vi\u1ec7c \u0111i k\u00fd k\u1ebft th\u00eam t\u1eadn 10 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cTh\u1eadt d\u1ec5 th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0m sao khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ch\u00ednh ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh xo\u00e0nh xo\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea5y, c\u00e1c anh n\u00f3i th\u00ec d\u1ec5 l\u1eafm, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi c\u00e1c anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m, kh\u00f4ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed HLV kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed7i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1ec1 l\u00e2u v\u1ec1 d\u00e0i v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a CLB. Ai ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e2y? C\u00e1c anh sao? Kh\u00f4ng, l\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u1ee9!\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cN\u00f3i chung, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n h\u1ebft c\u1ea3 b\u1edfi quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i mua ai, \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ch\u00fang ta khi b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111i theo m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2478","checkdouble":"194706"},{"date":"23:25 17/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/tan-binh-tai-tieng-cua-barca-hanh-phuc-sau-man-chao-san-camp-nou.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Malcom kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa khi s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh si\u00eau sao Leo Messi v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ghi b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Boca Juniors.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean tranh c\u00fap Joan Gamper</span> (<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1edb s\u00e1ng l\u1eadp vi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Barcelona) n\u0103m nay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t b\u1edfi m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh Malcom, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Bordeaux v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 41 tri\u1ec7u Euro, g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i b\u1edfi m\u00e0n l\u1eadt k\u00e8o Roma.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Malcom c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Malcom c\u1ee7a Barca h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau m\u00e0n ch\u00e0o s\u00e2n Camp Nou h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/malcom-toi-luon-muon-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n binh Malcom c\u1ee7a Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c Cules ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Malcom ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Boca Juniors, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea5y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o nh\u1ea5t. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u1ea1nh b\u00ean si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Leo Messi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00e2n th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Barca sau khi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i 21: \u201cT\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Messi, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. C\u00f2n g\u00ec tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u1ef9 m\u00e3n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi t\u00f4i ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft s\u00e2n Camp Nou, v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh anh \u1ea5y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">\u201cGi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c th\u1eadt r\u1ed3i, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu hay kh\u00f4ng \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa. N\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u00e0ng h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf La Liga v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Barcelona s\u1ebd m\u1edf m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Deportivo Alaves.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\">Malcom \u2013 Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Barcelona</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft AS Roma. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Barca s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Malcom nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh?</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2477","checkdouble":"194707"},{"date":"23:27 17/08","title":"HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Malaysia?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-olympic-malaysia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u00f4ng Kim Hak-Bum \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh \u1edf th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho t\u1ea5 HCV t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y tuy nhi\u00ean, &nbsp;\u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a HLV Kim Hak-Bum l\u1ea1i tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 thua v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2 chung cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a &lsquo;nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa h\u1ed5 \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c1&rdquo;. V\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Kim Hak-Bum \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng xin l\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/AEN20180730005600315_01_i.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Kim Hak-Bum nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: &quot;H\u00f4m nay, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i qu\u00e1 ch\u1ee7 quan trong c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 xin \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n sinh n\u0103m 1960 cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 h\u00f4m nay kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 l\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1eeb s\u1edbm khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 h\u1ea5p t\u1ea5p. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ebd ra t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i x\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u h\u1ecd b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng C\u0110V H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eb7n l\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Indonesia \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. HLV Kim Hak-Bum c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8. H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u khi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i do thua k\u00e9m Malaysia v\u1ec1 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u. N\u1ebfu v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng F. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018-331-194701.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018-331-194701.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U23 Malaysia 2-1 U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u Asiad 2018 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd khi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/quang-hai-duoc-menh-danh-la-messi-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194685.html\">Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 'Messi Vi\u1ec7t Nam' \u1edf ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-noi-gi-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194684.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta-292-194680.html\">B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 t\u01a1i t\u1ea3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2476","checkdouble":"194708"},{"date":"00:08 18/08","title":"Thua s\u1ed1c Malaysia, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/11/thua-soc-malaysia-han-quoc-van-co-kha-nang-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo c\u00e1ch chia b\u1ea3ng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi x\u1ea3y ra.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1i 17/8 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E, \u0110T Olympic Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kyrgyzstan b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua s\u1ed1c Malaysia, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua s\u1ed1c Malaysia, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/11/Dieu-gi-giup-U23-Viet-Nam-dang-choi-an-tuong-o-U23-chau-A-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y,\u00a0Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, k\u00e9m Malaysia 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Malaysia \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i x\u1ebfp sau do thua th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E l\u00e0 Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Bahrain c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a nhau, Olympic Malaysia \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u2018c\u00f2n gi\u00fap\u2019 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u00ednh to\u00e1n ban \u0111\u1ea7u, n\u1ebfu H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E c\u00f2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D, hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau. Song v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p Malaysia n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng D khi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ASIAD bang E\" title=\"ASIAD b\u1ea3ng E\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/1.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o tay Malaysia \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf m\u1ed9t trong c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B/E/F.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, th\u00ec c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi th\u00eam ba \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng x\u1ea3y ra l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Bahrain kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng Malaysia. Khi \u0111\u00f3 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng E.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ASIAD\" title=\"ASIAD\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/VN-HQ.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng B/E/F</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng/thua sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Kim chi ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m 4 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1eadn H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c vs Vi\u1ec7t Nam di\u1ec5n ra s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n t\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n l\u00e0: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng B b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c thua t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 Bahrain kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng Malaysia. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu 1 trong 4 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra th\u00ec Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8. T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-olympic-malaysia-168-194708.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-olympic-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-olympic-malaysia-168-194708.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Malaysia?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, \u00f4ng Kim Hak-Bum \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng ra nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh \u1edf th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018-331-194701.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-u23-malaysia-21-u23-han-quoc-asiad-2018-331-194701.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U23 Malaysia 2-1 U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u Asiad 2018 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd khi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2475","checkdouble":"194711"},{"date":"01:49 18/08","title":"Pogba \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man Utd t\u1eeb l\u00fac m\u1edbi v\u1ec1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/pogba-dang-le-phai-lam-doi-truong-man-utd-tu-luc-moi-ve.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Scholes mong mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Paul Pogba \u0111ang l\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf Old Trafford khi b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p phong \u0111\u1ed9 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018/19, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 \u00edt c\u00f3 y\u00ean \u1ea3 v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 k\u00e9o theo chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111i \u1edf ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Scholes HLV Mourinho n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng MU t\u1eeb khi m\u1edbi v\u1ec1  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Scholes HLV Mourinho n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng MU t\u1eeb khi m\u1edbi v\u1ec1  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Scholes-HLV-Mourinho-nen-de-Pogba-doi-truong-MU-tu-khi-moi-ve--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Mourinho n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng MU t\u1eeb hai n\u0103m qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Scholes v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a anh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf: \u201cCh\u00fang ta c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecdc v\u00e0 nghe v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng lung lay v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1 gi\u1eefa Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba, tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng n\u00e0o?\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang ta ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 Pogba c\u1ea7n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn hay r\u1ed3i 3-4 tr\u1eadn d\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t, c\u00f3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 t\u1eeb th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3, Pogba c\u00f9ng MU s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecf \u0111i n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 ngay \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba ng\u00e0y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y. H\u00e3y cho g\u00e3 trai tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00f3 th\u00eam tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m \u00e1p l\u1ef1c m\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y, ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh h\u01a1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3 c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-doi-roi-man-utd-ai-la-ke-dung-sau-giat-day-172-194179.html\">Paul Pogba \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Man Utd: Ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb \u0111\u1ee9ng sau gi\u1eadt d\u00e2y?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/truoc-mua-bong-thu-3-cua-mourinho-thanh-bai-tai-pogba-172-192011.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Mourinho \u1edf M.U: Th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-tran-mu-21-leicester-bong-dang-sieu-doi-truong-xuat-hien-172-194228.html\">M.U 2-1 Leicester: B\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng \u201cSi\u00eau \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2474","checkdouble":"194712"},{"date":"01:23 18/08","title":"De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, Pep Guardiola khuy\u00ean... chia tay Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/de-bruyne-chan-thuong-nang-pep-guardiola-khuyen-tam-chia-tay-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau khi \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn hung tin v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Etihad.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.1pt;\">Man City m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn hung tin khi Kevin De Bruyne d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t s\u00e2n Etihad n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nghi thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong v\u00f2ng ba th\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, Guardiola khuy\u00ean chia tay Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, Guardiola khuy\u00ean chia tay Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/de-bruyne-chan-thuong-nang-pep-guardiola-khuyen-tam-chia-tay-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kevin De Bruyne ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, HLV Pep Guardiola khuy\u00ean... t\u1ea1m chia tay Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">HLV Pep Guardiola nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng, v\u1eeba nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn l\u00fd do qu\u00e1 t\u1ea3i t\u1eeb World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n cho De Bruyne, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n x\u1ee9 Catalonia: \u201cCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1eddng khi anh \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t 11 th\u00e1ng tr\u1eddi. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng r\u1ed3i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 World Cup trong h\u00e8. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, trong khi con ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ef1ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">\u201cL\u1eddi khuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i cho ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed n\u00ean t\u1ea1m r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Man City trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi m\u00e0 \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3 h\u01a1i trong 2-3 tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m th\u1ebf ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng tay giang r\u1ed9ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Man City s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Huddersfield Town. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Premier League 2018/19, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c h\u01a1n b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh Arsenal ngay t\u1ea1i Emirates.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";color:black;letter-spacing:.1pt\"=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2473","checkdouble":"194713"},{"date":"15:44 17/08","title":"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong nh\u00f3m \"h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n\" s\u1eafp b\u1ecb Liverpool thanh l\u00fd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/liverpool-sap-ban-ragnar-klavan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng di\u1ec5n ra, Ragnar Klavan s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Liverpool trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u01a1n.</h2><h2>Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Goal \u0111\u01b0a tin, Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan cho Cagliari v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 2 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (2.5 tri\u1ec7u euro). Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Estonia s\u1ebd bay sang Italia trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ebb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Cagliari.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/liverpool-sap-ban-ragnar-klavan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Liverpool s\u1eafp b\u00e1n Ragnar Klavan cho Cagliari.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRagnar Klavan gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool n\u0103m 2016, ra s\u00e2n 53 tr\u1eadn sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Van Dijk, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Joe Gomez c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 khi\u1ebfn HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n Klavan n\u1eefa. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Jurgen Klopp c\u00f2n c\u00f3 hai trung v\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Dejan Lovren v\u00e0 Joel Matip.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 b\u1edfi trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Newcastle \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n mua Klavan nh\u01b0ng Jurgen Klopp kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool thanh l\u00fd h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ragnar Klavan, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c ra \u0111i l\u00e0 Danny Ward, Jon Flanagan v\u00e0 Emre Can. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, The Kop v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong di\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i l\u00e0 Simon Mignolet, Lazar Markovic, Pedro Chirivella, Marko Grujic v\u00e0 Divock Origi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi h\u01a1n 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed1n t\u00e2n binh, l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong tay HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf c\u1ea3 ba tuy\u1ebfn. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Liverpool \u0111ang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft ra \u0111i v\u1eeba thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed, v\u1eeba t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho HLV Jurgen Klopp trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League g\u1eb7p West Ham, Liverpool gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Premier League.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-cai-ten-tiep-theo-roi-liverpool-o-he-2018-172-194419.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-tu-choi-ban-hang-thai-cho-newcastle-172-194271.html\">HLV Klopp t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i cho Newcastle</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ghi-ban-phut-bu-gio-klavan-di-vao-lich-su-premier-league-172-176760.html\">Ghi b\u00e0n ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, sao Liverpool \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed NHA</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-liverpool-to-salah-tron-tap-luyen-172-173564.html\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1 Salah tr\u1ed1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u1edf Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-liverpool-len-tieng-thach-thuc-sergio-aguero-172-156173.html\">Sao Liverpool l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Sergio Aguero</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klavan-su-canh-tranh-vi-tri-la-tot-cho-liverpool-172-139137.html\">Klavan: S\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t cho Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)\u00a0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2472","checkdouble":"194675"},{"date":"15:38 17/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/u23-indonesia-vs-u23-lao-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Indonesia vs Olympic L\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng A Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/8.</h2>(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Palestine khi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng L\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i (20/8) th\u00ec m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi L\u00e0o kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean U23 L\u00e0o s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tinh th\u1ea7n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i song so s\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u1ee9 Tri\u1ec7u Voi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi U23 Indonesia quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng. U23 L\u00e0o ch\u1ec9 th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p 1. Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, h\u1ecd hay b\u1ecb xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c b\u00e0n thua l\u00e3ng x\u1eb9t.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 h\u00f4m nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/nhan-dinh-u23-indonesia-vs-u23-lao-19h-ngay-178-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Indonesia vs U23 L\u00e0o</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Indonesia c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft khai th\u00e1c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi ti\u1ebft: Indonesia lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ef1c hay v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eafng theo ki\u1ec3u h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t m\u1ed7i khi g\u1eb7p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1. <br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2471","checkdouble":"194676"},{"date":"15:41 17/08","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.\r\n\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV\u00a0Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eb7p Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng D t\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u01b0 h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.\u00a0</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng n\u00f3i: <em>\"T\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa khi c\u00f9ng Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n tranh ch\u1ea5p ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D. T\u1eeb l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u00e2n t\u00edch k\u0129 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t\".</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 HLV Park Hang-seo v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D l\u00e0 b\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n n\u00e9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E l\u00e0 Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang-seo \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng E.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Park n\u00f3i th\u00eam: <em>\"H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edbm g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi h\u1ecd \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n hay b\u1ea5t k\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng th\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. V\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam - Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd c\u0103ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft\".</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\"T\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00e0 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00f4i. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m h\u1ebft tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam\",</em> v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u00f4ng D\u01b0\u01a1ng V\u0169 L\u00e2m \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt c\u00f2n \u00edt kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-292-194674.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/tien-ve-quang-hai-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-292-194674.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Quang H\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 tin cho bi\u1ebft c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2470","checkdouble":"194677"},{"date":"15:44 17/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Malaysia vs U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 19h00 ng\u00e0y 17/8 (Asiad 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/u23-malaysia-vs-u23-han-quoc-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Malaysia vs U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Malaysia vs Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c b\u1ea3ng E Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 17/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5m HCV m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng khi \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p U23 Bahrain t\u1edbi 6-0 d\u00f9 ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Son Heung Min.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHwang Ui-jo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi hattrick. Na Sang Ho c\u0169ng c\u00f3 2 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 2 b\u00e0n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Kim Jin Ya v\u00e0 Hwang Hee Chan. L\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \"Ronaldo x\u1ee9 H\u00e0n\" v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb b\u1edfi U23 Malaysia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n U23 Bahrain n\u00ean U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eeba kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Malaysia vs U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Malaysia vs U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Asiad 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/nhan-dinh-u23-malaysia-vs-u23-han-quoc-19h00-ngay-178-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Malaysia vs U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e1ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd th\u1eafng U23 Malaysia v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t bao nhi\u00eau m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u00a0 U23 Malaysia c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Asiad 2018 nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eb3ng ai d\u00e1m tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a U23 Malaysia tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. M\u1ed1i th\u00f9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD 2014 (t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) c\u1ee7a U23 Malaysia kh\u00f3 m\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f2i.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2469","checkdouble":"194678"},{"date":"16:22 17/08","title":"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 t\u01a1i t\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</h2><h2>B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau hai tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean gi\u00e0nh su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng Th\u00e1i Lan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed su\u00fdt thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 Bangladesh.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bao Thai Lan khen Olympic Viet Nam sau man trinh dien khong tot cua doi tuyen nuoc nay.\" title=\"B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/bao-thai-lan-khen-olympic-viet-nam-che-doi-nha-toi-ta.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh t\u00edch tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3, b\u00e1o Th\u00e1i Lan khen Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. T\u1edd Khaosod vi\u1ebft: &quot;L\u1ee9a U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111ang ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i sau khi \u0111o\u1ea1t HCV SEA Games 29, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111ang thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Worrawoot ch\u01b0a th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o qua hai tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u00f2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb ch\u00ea t\u01a1i t\u1ea3<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111ang b\u1ecb thu h\u1eb9p khi h\u1ecd m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Olympic Uzbekistan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i. N\u1ebfu thua tr\u1eadn, Th\u00e1i Lan nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i trong vi\u1ec7c so th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n&quot; l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean SiamSport. T\u1edd n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfc l\u1eddi ch\u00ea th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Worrawoot: &quot;L\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan qu\u00e1 c\u1ea7u to\u00e0n, thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Bangladesh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng HLV Worrawoot ch\u1eb3ng th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;S\u1ef1 ch\u1ee7 quan c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua. N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfn xa, \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng khi Chenrop Samphaodi \u0111ang sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9&quot;.<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-olympic-viet-nam-danh-gia-cau-thu-nhat-non-kinh-nghiem-168-194677.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-lang-tranh-truyen-thong-que-nha-sau-tran-thang-nepal-168-194673.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo l\u1ea3ng tr\u00e1nh truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nepal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-han-quoc-dung-ve-phia-viet-nam-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194671.html\">B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/bat-dong-noi-bo-olympic-nepal-da-tu-thua-viet-nam-ngay-truoc-tran-472-194637.html\">B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, Olympic Nepal \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 thua Vi\u1ec7t Nam ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-gap-nhat-ban-khi-chien-thang-khong-con-qua-xa-xi-168-194634.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Khi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 xa x\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-dung-tinh-toan-nhieu-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban-168-194633.html\">&ldquo;Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eebng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2468","checkdouble":"194680"}]}